name: Bolingu
description:
Recorded today, 5.31 PM, on Thursday, 9 September 2021, in the heart of Borneo, consist of my voice and a lute instrument called Sape from Kalimantan island. The piece called “Bolingu” means “longing”. 

Everyone who purchased this piece will be invited to a zoom live performance. Find out more on my Twitter account @baseputbaseput
